  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-CON-03 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification is performed. This package carries a future-dated evidence node (W-CON-03): one ValidationResult bears an evidenceTimestamp in 2027, two years after the UnitOfAssurance signatureTimestamp of 2024, creating a temporal consistency violation that is not addressed in the narrative.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/morrison-cou2-hemolysis-requirement",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/morrison-cou2-hemolysis-claim",
