      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Version-controlled solver with documented regression test suite covering hemolysis-relevant flow regimes; ISO 9001-aligned QMS in place.",
      "rationale": "The CFD solver (ANSYS Fluent 2023 R1) is version-controlled and regression-tested for standard benchmark cases. However, no hemolysis-specific regression suite exists and the QMS documentation does not cover user-defined function (UDF) code used for the hemolysis power-law model. Achieved level 3 falls short of required level 4."
    },
    {
