      "factorType": "Numerical code verification",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Method of manufactured solutions (MMS) or equivalent analytical verification for all governing equations including scalar hemolysis transport.",
      "rationale": "MMS verification was completed for the Navier-Stokes equations and the k-omega turbulence closure. The hemolysis scalar transport UDF was not independently verified via MMS. Achieved level 3 is below the required level 4 for MRL 5."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Discretization error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 4,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "GCI less than 5% on hemolysis QoI using at least three systematically refined meshes with refinement ratio greater than 1.3.",
      "rationale": "Three meshes with refinement ratio 1.58 were used. GCI on the fine mesh is 3.8% for the hemolysis index QoI, satisfying the 5% threshold. Achieved level matches required level 4."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Test conditions",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
