      "rationale": "Validation uses the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry, which is not the clinical VAD geometry. Operating conditions partially overlap the COU envelope but the highest speed condition (3600 RPM) in the COU was not included in the validation study. Achieved level 3 is below required level 4."
